2475/264167/4272?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.com%2Fbullet-for-my-valentine-tickets%2Fartist%2F1009824" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Ticketmaster</a>进行预售。在这里查看官方巡演海报： </p><figure id="attachment_3794702" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3794702" style="width: 1080px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3794702" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/The-Poisoned-Ascendancy-Tour-North-America-poster-2025.jpeg" alt="Bullet For My Valentine 和 Trivium 2025 年“Poisoned Ascendancy”北美巡演海报" width="1080" height="1350" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/The-Poisoned-Ascendancy-Tour-North-America-poster-2025.jpeg 1080w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/The-Poisoned-Ascendancy-Tour-North-America-poster-2025-400x500.jpeg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/The-Poisoned-Ascendancy-Tour-North-America-poster-2025-800x1000.jpeg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/The-Poisoned-Ascendancy-Tour-North-America-poster-2025-696x870.jpeg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/The-Poisoned-Ascendancy-Tour-North-America-poster-2025-1068x1335.jpeg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 1080px) 100vw, 1080px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3794702" class="wp-caption-text"> Bullet For My Valentine 和 Trivium 2025 年“Poisoned Ascendancy”北美巡演。图片来源：新闻界</figcaption></figure><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="550" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">与<a href="https://twitter.com/augustburnsred?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">@augustburnsred</a> @sylosisofficial 和<a href="https://twitter.com/BleedFromWithin?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">@bleedfromwithin</a>一起的美国中毒优势之旅。如果您已注册我们的邮件程序，预售代码将从明天开始发送，一般销售将于周五上午 10 点开始。</p><p>在此注册预售： <a href="https://t.co/W7lkSc57yR">https://t.co/W7lkSc57yR</a> <a href="https://t.co/NQHlN55Jh2">pic.twitter.com/NQHlN55Jh2</a></p><p> — BFMV (@bfmvofficial) <a href="https://twitter.com/bfmvofficial/status/18360424272887